"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Functions for Alpha Numeric Tag-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on KeyPress of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumCharsOnPress(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumCharsOnPress_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumChars(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"

"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"

"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"

"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"

"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern=  new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_leng"
"th+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function revGenricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  unicode_value;\r\n"
"\tvar unicode_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + unicode_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code which you want to check\r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genericMap(char_code,code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= code_0 ) && ( char_code <= code_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_0 + ( char_code - code_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == code_decimal) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code w"

"function makeRegEx2(fmt2)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"
"\t   alert(\"no fomat specified\");\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"

"\r\n"

"\t\t\t}\r\n"

"\r\n"

"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=fmt2.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(index+1,fmt2.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"

"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tpattern1=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern2=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern3=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern4=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern5=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>40 && charCode<46)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>57 && charCode<65)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if (charCode>64 && charCode<91)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode==47)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\t\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tif( txt ==\"\") return true;\r\n"
"\t\tif(pattern2 !=null&&pattern2 !=\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t if( true == pattern2.test(txt.toString()) ) return true;\r\n"

*** [tid=e81c	Action	116] Receiving response from host 9.161.154.14:80 ( 3/6/2008 09:04:30 )

"count=0;\r\n"
"/************************************************************************\r\n"
"* This is master file which contain the generic coversion function \r\n"
"*  and other objects used for conversion process\r\n"
"*  author : Imtiyaz Baig\r\n"
"**************************************************************************/ \r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/***********************************************************************\r\n"
"* Constructor for DecimalMap object\r\n"
"* arg1(code_0) - unicode charcter value of 0 for that language\r\n"
"* arg1(code_9) - unicode charcter value of 9 for that language\r\n"
"* arg1(code_decimal) - unicode charcter value of . for that language\r\n"
"*************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function  DecimalMap(code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tthis.CODE_0=code_0;\r\n"
"\tthis.CODE_9=code_9;\r\n"
"\tthis.CODE_DECIMAL=co"


*** [tid=e81c	Action	116] Receiving response from host 9.161.154.14:80 ( 3/6/2008 09:04:30 )

"de_decimal;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"HINDI=new DecimalMap(2406,2415,46);\r\n"
"ARABIC= new DecimalMap(1632,1641,1643);\r\n"
"SPANISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"
"*******************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"

"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"

"}\r\n"

"* function generic decimal map \r\n"

"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genericMap(char_code,code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= code_0 ) && ( char_code <= code_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_0 + ( char_code - code_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == code_decimal) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"

"function makeRegEx2(fmt2)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"

"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=fmt2.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(index+1,fmt2.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length2=fmt2.substring(index+1,fmt2.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tpattern1=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern2=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern3=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern4=\"\";\r\n"

"\r\n"

"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"HINDI=new DecimalMap(2406,2415,46);\r\n"
"ARABIC= new DecimalMap(1632,1641,1643);\r\n"
"SPANISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"
"*******************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern=  new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_leng"
"th+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function revGenricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  unicode_value;\r\n"
"\tvar unicode_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + unicode_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code which you want to check\r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genericMap(char_code,code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= code_0 ) && ( char_code <= code_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_0 + ( char_code - code_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == code_decimal) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"

"function makeRegEx2(fmt2)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif ( fmt2 ==  \"\")\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t   alert(\"no fomat specified\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt2=fmt2.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt2.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=fmt2;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length2=fmt2.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt2.substring(index+1,fmt2.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length2=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length2=fmt2.substring(index+1,fmt2.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tpattern1=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern2=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern3=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern4=\"\";\r\n"
"\tpattern5=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length2 ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length2 == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern1= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length2 ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length2 != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern2= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length2+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length2 != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length2 ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern3= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length2+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length2+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\tpattern3= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length2+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tpattern4= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length2+\"}[\\.]$\");\r\n"
"\t\tpattern5= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length2+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_len"
"gth2+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"

"\t\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\t\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\t\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\t\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(charCode>96 && charCode<123 )\r\n"
"\t{\t\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>90 && charCode<97)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>122 && charCode<127)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>=32 && charCode<37)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>40 && charCode<46)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"

"\t{\r\n"

"         if (month == 2) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"            var leap = (year % 4 == 0 &&\r\n"
"               (year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0));\r\n"
"            if (day < 1 || day>29 || (day == 29 && !leap)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t//alert(\"Please Enter the correct number of days for the february month\");\r\n"
"                return false;\r\n"
"            }\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t return true;\r\n"
"    }\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function numbersonly(myfield, e, dec)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"var key;\r\n"
"var keychar;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"if (window.event)\r\n"
"   key = window.event.keyCode;\r\n"
"else if (e)\r\n"
"   key = e.which;\r\n"
"else\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"keychar = String.fromCharCode(key);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// control keys\r\n"
"if ((key==null) || (key==0) || (key==8) || \r\n"
"    (key==9) || (key==27) )\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// numbers\r\n"
"else if (((\"0123456789\").indexOf(keychar) > -1))\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// decimal point jump\r\n"
"else if (dec && (keychar == \".\"))\r\n"
"   {\r\n"
"   myfield.form.elements[dec].focus();\r\n"
"   return false;\r\n"
"   }\r\n"
"else\r\n"
"   return false;\r\n"
"}"

"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"

"\t}\r\n"

"function  FnCheckNumChars(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"

"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"

"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"

"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"

"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"

"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Functions for Alpha Numeric Tag-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on KeyPress of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumCharsOnPress(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumCharsOnPress_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumChars(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"

"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"

"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"

"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"

"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"

"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
