"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"

"\tif(eval(func)==false) {\r\n"

"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"

"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is called by the Locale specific Keypress function.\r\n"
"*This Function takes the Minimum and Maximum Keycodes for the \r\n"
"*numbers and restricts the user from entering other KeyCodes\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberOnPressValue(evt,min,max) {\r\n"
"\tvar keyCodePress = (window.event)?event.keyCode:evt.which;\r\n"
"\tif(keyCodePress< min || keyCodePress> max) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(keyCodePress==8 || keyCodePress==0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fals"

"\t\t}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of Number tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumber_\"+locale+\"(event,min,max,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\tif(eval(func)==false) {\r\n"
"\t\tobjTextField.focus();\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"}\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Functions for Alpha Numeric Tag-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on KeyPress of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumCharsOnPress(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumCharsOnPress_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"

"*This is the Function called on Blur of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumChars(event,objTextField) {\r\n"

"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"

"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"

"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"

"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"HINDI=new DecimalMap(2406,2415,46);\r\n"
"ARABIC= new DecimalMap(1632,1641,1643);\r\n"
"SPANISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"
"*******************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern=  new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_leng"
"th+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"

"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"

"function makeRegEx2(fmt2)\r\n"
"{\r\n"

"{\r\n"

"function  DecimalMap(code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tthis.CODE_0=code_0;\r\n"
"\tthis.CODE_9=code_9;\r\n"

*** [tid=18c68	Action1	74] Receiving response from host 9.161.154.14:80 ( 3/6/2008 09:53:04 )

"de_decimal;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"HINDI=new DecimalMap(2406,2415,46);\r\n"
"ARABIC= new DecimalMap(1632,1641,1643);\r\n"
"SPANISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"
"*******************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern=  new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_leng"
"th+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function revGenricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  unicode_value;\r\n"
"\tvar unicode_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + unicode_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code which you want to check\r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genericMap(char_code,code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= code_0 ) && ( char_code <= code_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_0 + ( char_code - code_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == code_decimal) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code which you want to check\r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function RevGenericMap(char_code,code_0,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= ENGLISH.CODE_0 ) && ( char_code <= ENGLISH.CODE_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn code_0 + ( char_code - ENGLISH.CODE_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function checkDecimal\r\n"

"/***************************************************************************\r\n"
"* Next create objects for language which has mapping to ascii decimal system\r\n"
"* These interun will be used in function to remove the magic numbers from the\r\n"
"* code\r\n"
"****************************************************************************/\r\n"
"ENGLISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"HINDI=new DecimalMap(2406,2415,46);\r\n"
"ARABIC= new DecimalMap(1632,1641,1643);\r\n"
"SPANISH= new DecimalMap(48,57,46);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/****************************************************************************\r\n"
"*  main function to do the validation \r\n"
"*  arg1(element) - element is the text box for which you are doing validation\r\n"
"*  arg2(min) - Min value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg3(max) - Max value it can take \r\n"
"*  arg4(fmt)  - decimal number format e.g.   if you pass fmt=\"2.2\"  it will \r\n"
"                 validate numbers two digits before  decimal  and two\r\n"
"                  digits after decimal\r\n"
"*   usage - This is main function called to perform the lacole based validation\r\n"
"*******************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function doValidation(element,min,max,fmt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif( txt == \"\" ) return true;\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(txt == \".\"||txt == \"0.\"||txt == \".0\") element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tvar patt0= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt1= new RegExp(\"^[0]*[\\.]{0,1}$\");\r\n"
"\tvar patt2= new RegExp(\"^[\\.]{0,1}[0]*$\");\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt0.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt1.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tif( true == patt2.test(txt.toString()) ) element.value=\"0\";\r\n"
"\tfirstTimekeyPress=true\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\treturn true;\r\n"
"\t//call to form the regular expression\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx(fmt,txt);\r\n"
"    try\r\n"
"    {\r\n"
"\t\treturn eval(locale + \"_validate( txt , \" + min + \",\" + max + \")\" ); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tcatch ( e )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t//most probabely language not supported \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/******************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : makeRegEx\r\n"
"*  arg1(fmt) - Format of the decimal point  e.g you can pass \"2.2\" ,\"2\" ,\".2\" etc\r\n"
"* usage - used to form the regular expression based on the format\r\n"
"*********************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function makeRegEx(fmt,txt)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t//extract the digit before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\tif(fmt==null)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=txt;\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(\"Please enter correct format\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tfmt=fmt.toString();\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=fmt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 == index)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt  < 1 ) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t   whole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\"\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(0, index) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twhole_part_length=fmt.substring(0, index);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\tif ( fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length) < 1 )\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tfraction_part_length=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t    fraction_part_length=fmt.substring(index+1,fmt.length);\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(( whole_part_length ==  \"\" ) && ( fraction_part_length == \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t// if nothing is specified then assume any number before decimal and after decimal\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]*[\\.]{0,1}[0-9]*$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length ==  \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length != \"\" ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_length+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( ( whole_part_length != \"\" )  && ( fraction_part_length ==  \"\"  ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tpattern= new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}$\");\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tpattern=  new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,\"+whole_part_length+\"}[\\.][0-9]{1,\"+fraction_part_leng"
"th+\"}$\"); \r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"/**************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function name : genricConvertor\r\n"
"* arg1(txt) - string in other language \r\n"
"* arg2(convertor) - convertor function for that language\r\n"
"* usage - convert the decimal valused form other language to ASCII\r\n"
"*****************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function revGenricConvertor(txt,convertor)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  unicode_value;\r\n"
"\tvar unicode_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<txt.length;i++)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=txt.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_value=eval(\"convertor(\" + char_code + \")\");\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + unicode_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tunicode_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code which you want to check\r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - this  function convert decimal character  from other language to ascii\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"function genericMap(char_code,code_0,code_9,code_decimal)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tif( ( char_code >= code_0 ) && ( char_code <= code_9 ) )\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_0 + ( char_code - code_0);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if ( char_code == code_decimal) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn ENGLISH.CODE_DECIMAL;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/*************************************************************************************\r\n"
"* function generic decimal map \r\n"
"* arg1 (char_code) - character code w"

"* function genericOnkeyPress\r\n"
"* arg1 (e) - event object \r\n"
"* arg2 (code_0) - code of character 0 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg3 (code-9) - code of character 9 in specified language\r\n"
"* arg4 (code_decimal) - code of character . in specified language\r\n"
"* usage - This function is called when key is pressed while focus is in inputbox\r\n"
"***************************************************************************************/\r\n"
"\r\n"
"function genericOnkeyPress(fmt,element ,e,code_0,code_9,decimal_code)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"\tcount=0;\r\n"
"\tmakeRegEx2(fmt);\r\n"
"\t e = (e) ? e : event;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tvar  charCode= (e.intCode) ? e.intCode : ((e.keyCode) ? e.keyCode : ((e.which) ? e.which : 0"
"));\r\n"
"\t\tvar txt=element.value;\r\n"
"\t\tvar index=txt.indexOf('.');\r\n"
"\t\tif ( -1 != index && charCode==46 ) return false;\r\n"
"\t//alert(\"charCode1=\"+charCode);\t\r\n"
"\tif( charCode ==13 || charCode ==110 || charCode ==190)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\tif(txt == \".\") element.value=\"0.\";\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\tif(charCode == 190)\r\n"
"\t{\t\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tif(charCode>105 && charCode<123 )\r\n"
"\t{\t\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>90 && charCode<96)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>122 && charCode<127)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>=32 && charCode<46)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode>57 && charCode<65)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if (charCode>64 && charCode<91)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse if(charCode==47)\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t  //    alert(\"element should be in range \"+min+\" - to - \" +max );\r\n"
"\t\t\t  eval(locale + \"_AlertRange(min,max)\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t  return false;\t\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t   var format=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\tfor ( i = 0 ; i < whole_part_length ; i++)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t format += \"X\"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif (fraction_part_length > 1)\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\tformat += \".\";\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor ( i = 0 ; i < fraction_part_length ; i++)\r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t format += \"X\"\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\teval(locale+ \"_Alertformat(format)\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t  \r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"

"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"

"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"

"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"

"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of Number tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumber_\"+locale+\"(event,min,max,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\tif(eval(func)==false) {\r\n"
"\t\tobjTextField.focus();\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Functions for Alpha Numeric Tag-->\r\n"

"function  FnCheckNumCharsOnPress(event,objTextField) {\r\n"

"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"

"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of Number tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumber_\"+locale+\"(event,min,max,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\tif(eval(func)==false) {\r\n"
"\t\tobjTextField.focus();\r\n"
"\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Functions for Alpha Numeric Tag-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on KeyPress of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumCharsOnPress(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumCharsOnPress_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This is the Function called on Blur of AlphaNumberic tag.\r\n"
"*This Function calls the locale specific Function \r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function  FnCheckNumChars(event,objTextField) {\r\n"
"\tvar locale = document.all.h_user_locale.value;\r\n"
"\tvar func=\"FnCheckNumChars_\"+locale+\"(event,objTextField)\";\r\n"
"\treturn eval(func);\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedCount = 0;\r\n"
"\t\tvar i;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(selectedCount>1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Edit only one value at a time\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tif(theSelFrom.options[i].selected) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedCount++;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedText = theSelFrom.options[i].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tselectedValues = theSelFrom.options[i].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tdeleteOption(theSelFrom, i);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tvar splitValue=selectedValues.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(splitValue[0]==splitValue[1]) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t\t        \t\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\ttheSelTo.value=selectedText;\r\n"
"\t        \t\t\t\ttheHidValue.value=selectedValues;\r\n"
"        \t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        \t\t\treturn true;\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction addOption(theSel, theText, theValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar newOpt = new Option(theText, theValue);\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength] = newOpt;\r\n"
"\t\ttheSel.options[selLength].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction selectAll(theSelFrom) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tfor(i=selLength-1; i>=0; i--) \r\n"
"\t\t\ttheSelFrom.options[i].selected=true;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction deleteOption(theSel, theIndex) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSel.length;\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(selLength>0) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\ttheSel.options[theIndex] = null;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnSelectToolTip (event) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar obj = event.srcElement;\r\n"
"        with(document.getElementById(\"s1\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif(obj.selectedIndex!=-1) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tinnerHTML = obj.options[obj.selectedIndex].text;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\twith(style) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseout\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"none\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tif(event.type == \"mouseover\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplay = \"inline\";\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttop = event.y-10;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"rom the combo box\r\n"
"\tfunction displayAmount(listBox, textBox ){\r\n"
"\t\t//The fee combo box\r\n"
"\t\tvar comboBox = document.getElementsByName(listBox)[0];\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t//The amount text box\r\n"
"\t\tvar amountField = document.getElementsByName(textBox)[0];\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t//If no fee is selected then the amount field displays nothing\r\n"
"\t\tif(comboBox.selectedIndex==0)\r\n"
"\t\t\tamountField.value = \"\";\r\n"
"\t\telse{\r\n"

"\t\t\tif (centerCustActionForm.selectedFeeAmntList[indexSelectedFee]!= undefined){\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t//obtaining the fee amount for a particular fee\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tvar amount=centerCustActionForm.selectedFeeAmntList[indexSelectedFee].value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t//assigning the value of the fee amount to the text box\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tamountField.value = amount;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\telse{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\tamountField.value=centerCustActionForm.selectedFeeAmntList.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"

"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"

"function isValidDate(day, month, year) \r\n"
"\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t    if (month < 1 || month > 12) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t//alert(\"Please Enter the month in the range 1-12\");\r\n"
"            return false;\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"        \r\n"
"\t\tif (month==4 || month==6 || month==9 || month==11 )\r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\tif (day < 1 || day > 30) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t//alert(\"Please Enter the days in the range 1-30\");\r\n"
"            return false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t }\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\tif (month == 1 || month == 3 || month == 5 || month == 7 || month==8 || month ==10 || mont"
"h==12) \r\n"
"\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t\tif (day < 1 || day > 31) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\t//alert(\"Please Enter the days in the range 1-31\");\r\n"
"            return false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t }\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\r\n"
"         if (month == 2) \r\n"
"\t\t\t{\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"            var leap = (year % 4 == 0 &&\r\n"
"               (year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0));\r\n"
"            if (day < 1 || day>29 || (day == 29 && !leap)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\t//alert(\"Please Enter the correct number of days for the february month\");\r\n"
"                return false;\r\n"
"            }\r\n"
"        }\r\n"
"\t\t\r\n"
"\t\t return true;\r\n"
"    }\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"

"\r\n"
"function numbersonly(myfield, e, dec)\r\n"
"{\r\n"
"var key;\r\n"
"var keychar;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"if (window.event)\r\n"
"   key = window.event.keyCode;\r\n"
"else if (e)\r\n"
"   key = e.which;\r\n"
"else\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"keychar = String.fromCharCode(key);\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// control keys\r\n"
"if ((key==null) || (key==0) || (key==8) || \r\n"
"    (key==9) || (key==27) )\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// numbers\r\n"
"else if (((\"0123456789\").indexOf(keychar) > -1))\r\n"
"   return true;\r\n"
"\r\n"
"// decimal point jump\r\n"
"else if (dec && (keychar == \".\"))\r\n"
"   {\r\n"
"   myfield.form.elements[dec].focus();\r\n"
"   return false;\r\n"
"   }\r\n"
"else\r\n"
"   return false;\r\n"
"}"

"function  FnCheckNumber(event,min,max,objTextField) {\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"

"<!--Generic Convertor -->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to convert the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function genericConvertor(textValue,convertorMethod) {\r\n"
"\tvar  char_code;\r\n"
"\tvar  asci_value;\r\n"
"\tvar asci_txt=\"\";\r\n"
"\tfor(i=0;i<textValue.length;i++) {\r\n"
"\t\tchar_code=textValue.charCodeAt(i);\r\n"
"\t\tasci_value=eval(convertorMethod+\"(\"+char_code+\")\");\r\n"
"\t\toutput = eval(\"String.fromCharCode(\" + asci_value + \")\");\r\n"
"\t\tasci_txt += output;\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\treturn asci_txt;\r\n"
"}\t\r\n"
"\r\n"
"<!--Convertor Map-->\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function is used to map the numbers entered in language\r\n"
"*other than English to English.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function convertorMap(char_code,minDigit,maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\tif(char_code>=minDigit&&char_code<=maxDigit) {\r\n"
"\t\treturn 48+(char_code-minDigit);\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn char_code;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//--------------------Master Tag-------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n"
"\r\n"
"\tfunction fnAdd(theSel, theText,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tvar theValue;\r\n"
"\t\tif(theText.value==\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Enter value\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tif(theHidValue.value==\"\")\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=theText.value+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar val=theHidValue.value;\r\n"
"\t\t\tvar splitValue = val.split(\"_\");\r\n"
"\t\t\ttheValue=splitValue[0]+\"_\"+theText.value;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t//alert(theValue);\r\n"
"\t\taddOption(theSel,theText.value,theValue);\r\n"
"\t\ttheText.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t\ttheHidValue.value=\"\";\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\t\r\n"
"\tfunction fnEdit(theSelFrom, theSelTo,theHidValue) {\r\n"
"\t\tif(theSelTo.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add or Clear value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if(theHidValue.value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Add value in enter before Editing\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\tvar selLength = theSelFrom.length;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedText ;\r\n"
"\t\tvar selectedValues;\r\n"

"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*numbers only.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function FnCheckNumberEnglish(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tvar pattern=new RegExp(\"^[0-9]{1,}$\");\r\n"
"\t\tif(true==pattern.test(value.toString())) {\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value);\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse {\r\n"
"\t\t\talert(\"Numbers only\");\r\n"
"\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse\r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
"/**\r\n"
"*This Function checks if the Value entered in the Text box is\r\n"
"*in between the min and max specified.\r\n"
"*/\r\n"
"function fnCheckRange(event,min,max,value) {\r\n"
"\tif(value!=null && value!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\tif(min!=null && min!=\"\" && max!=null && max!=\"\") {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min) || (value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be between \"+min+\" and \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((min==null || min==\"\") && (max!=null && max!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value>max)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be less than \"+max);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\telse if((max==null || max==\"\") && (min!=null && min!=\"\")) {\r\n"
"\t\t\tif((value<min)) {\r\n"
"\t\t\t\talert(\"value should be greater than \"+min);\r\n"
"\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n"
"\t\t\t}\r\n"
"\t\t}\r\n"
"\t}\r\n"
"\telse \r\n"
"\t\treturn true;\r\n"
"}\r\n"
"\r\n"
